Aim: How we use python to generate web pages?
Internal Server Error - How to fix?
apache2 doesnt have the correct permissions to run the program.
Check permissions using $ ls -l . The other permissions should be: r--x
The python program is not configured to run on its own.
The python program has an error when run.
Both 2 and 3 should be mitigated by testing that the program runs on its own via a shell, if that works, they are not your problem.
The python program takes too long to run (~2 minutes)
Once again, running via the command line should allow you to rule this out.
